{"tid":1793971,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街老細","createTime":"2019-12-22T18:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T18:28:15.000Z","uid":225878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4090c3239f389c4a643f0475e7ab8ba2e998daa","tid":1793971,"uid":225878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"話說前排去左間所謂 gym room(係荔枝角)個到做Personal trainer，返咗1個月，個老細話公司冇生意所以要將我轉做pt，叫做係有客要教先返工咁既意思。咁好啦，之前有幾個客由頭到尾都跟我上堂，好記得佢講到明比我跟返自己嘅客，但轉個頭我D客同佢約時間上堂，佢就同人講會由其他教練教，咁姐係點？一獲過炒起我，咁之前所講既承諾係廢話啦。<br />\n<br />\n最撚搞笑係自己冇教練牌，走去幫人試堂係到亂鳩咁教，係隔離睇都笑撚咗出聲，咁有一日佢好叻仔試完堂，個客報左教練堂，除左試堂個堂，之後上堂又係我教，到最後分傭個陣，話張單係佢，我冇錢分架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當我做義工？<br />\n<br />\n我真係未遇過咁仆街既老細，咁當然仲有D嘢未講哂，我都唔好意思拎D小事出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d952abec133a228a5a8d18fb7e7022c516304773","tid":1793971,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:28:15.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi